org.spongepowered.api.event.item.inventory

Interface ChangeInventoryEvent.Pickup.Pre

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cancellable, Event, TargetEntityEvent, TargetInventoryEvent, TargetItemEvent
    Enclosing interface:
    ChangeInventoryEvent.Pickup

    public static interface ChangeInventoryEvent.Pickup.Pre
extends TargetInventoryEvent, TargetItemEvent, Cancellable
    Fires before an Item is picked up.

    Modifying the picked up items causes this event to be automatically canceled if the inventory does not fit the entire list.
